  m_TableData:
  - m_Id: 62963863552
    m_Localized: Los Timos Echos
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5028134801408
    m_Localized: (ES) Create a Time Echo of yourself. The Echo distracts enemies.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5453898600448
    m_Localized: '{0:plural:(ES) Requirement|(ES) Requirements}:'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
      - rid: 8822043155402850619
  - m_Id: 8055289827328
    m_Localized: (ES) Healing Wisp
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8189448835072
    m_Localized: (ES) When the Echo dies from an enemy attack, it releases a Healing
      Wisp that moves towards you and heals you on contact.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9992533987328
    m_Localized: (ES) Timeless Attack
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 10611357405184
    m_Localized: (ES) The Echo can perform 1 attack.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 10832615329792
    m_Localized: '- {0} {0:plural:(ES) Skill Point|(ES) Skill Points}'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
      - rid: 8822043155402850619
  - m_Id: 30062941327360
    m_Localized: '(ES) Locks out:'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 35472238727168
    m_Localized: (ES) You've taken a different path - this skill is now locked.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 597578642116608
    m_Localized: (ES) Cleanse
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 598631206899712
    m_Localized: (ES) Healing Wisp additionally reduces the duration of negative
      status effects by 1 second.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 599290018811904
    m_Localized: (ES) Quick Thinking
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 599766001012736
    m_Localized: (ES) Healing Wisp additionaly reduces the cooldowns of your other
      skills by 1 second.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 642678751514624
    m_Localized: (ES) Quick Dash
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 642917143171072
    m_Localized: '(ES) Dash to avoid attacks.

      You cannot take damage while
      dashing.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 643901017837568
    m_Localized: (ES) Echo Step
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 644023281799168
    m_Localized: '(ES) Leave a Time Echo behind when performing Quick Dash.

      This
      Time Echo inherits all of its upgrades.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 646353288974336
    m_Localized: (ES) Deja Vu
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 646504741097472
    m_Localized: '(ES) Create a Time Echo on arrival when performing Quick Dash.

      This
      Time Echo inherits all of its upgrades.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 647539463311360
    m_Localized: (ES) Time Lost Shard
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 647686700158976
    m_Localized: '(ES) Leave a Time Shard behind when performing Quick Dash.

      This
      Time Shard inherits all of its upgrades.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 648191543365632
    m_Localized: (ES) Found Fragment
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 648303153795072
    m_Localized: '(ES) Create a Time Shard on arrival when performing Quick Dash.

      This
      Time Shard inherits all of its upgrades.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
